3The ssbdiagnose utility reports issues in SQL Server Service Broker
conversations, or in the configurations of Service Broker services.
Configuration checks can be made for a single service or two services.
Any errors found are reported either in the command prompt window in
human-readable text, or in formatted XML that can be redirected to a file
